  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "元年春正月，詔曰：「前日孝惠皇帝言欲除三族罪、妖言令，議未決而崩，今除之。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "二月，賜民爵，戶一級。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "初置孝弟力田二千石者一人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "夏五月丙申，趙王宮叢臺災。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "立孝惠後宮子強為淮陽王，不疑為恆山王，弘為襄城侯，朝為軹侯，武為壺關侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "秋，桃李華。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "二年春，詔曰：「高皇帝匡飭天下，諸有功者皆受分地為列侯，萬民大安，莫不受休德。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "朕思念至於久遠 而功名不著，亡以尊大誼，施後世。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "今欲差次列侯功以定朝位，臧于高廟，世世勿絕，嗣子各襲其功位。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "其與列侯議定奏之。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "丞相臣平言：「謹與絳侯臣勃、曲周 侯臣商、潁陰侯臣嬰、安國侯臣陵等議，列侯幸得賜餐錢奉邑，陛下加惠，以功次定朝位，臣請臧高廟。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "奏可。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "春正月乙卯，地震，羌道、武都道山崩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "夏六月丙 戌晦，日有蝕之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "秋七月，恆山王不疑薨。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "行八銖錢。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "三年夏，江水、溢，流民四千餘家。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "秋，星晝見。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "四年夏，少帝自知非皇后子，出怨言，皇太后幽之永巷。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "詔曰：「凡有天下治萬民者，蓋之如天，容之如 地；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "上有驩心以使百姓，百姓欣然以事其上，驩欣交通而天下治。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "今皇帝疾久不已，乃失惑昏亂，不能繼嗣奉宗廟，守祭祀，不可屬天下。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "其議代之。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "群臣皆曰： 「皇太后為天下計，所以安宗廟社稷甚深。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "頓首奉詔。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "五月丙辰，立恆山王弘為皇帝。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "五年春，南粵王尉佗自稱南武帝。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "秋八月，淮陽王彊薨。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "九月，發河東、上黨騎屯北地。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "六年春，星晝見。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "夏四月，赦天下。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "秩長陵令二千石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "六月，城長陵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "匈奴寇狄道，攻阿陽。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "行五分錢。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "八年春，封中謁者張釋卿為列侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "諸中官、宦者令丞皆賜爵關內侯，食邑。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "夏，江水、漢水溢，流萬餘家。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "秋七月辛巳，皇太后崩于未央宮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "遺詔賜諸侯王各千金，將相列侯下至郎吏各有差。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "大赦天下。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "上將軍祿、相國產顓兵秉政，自知背高皇帝約，恐為大臣諸侯王所誅，因謀作亂。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "時齊悼惠王子朱虛侯章 在京師，以祿女為婦，知其謀，乃使人告兄齊王，令發兵西。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "章欲與太尉勃、丞相平為內應，以誅諸呂。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "齊王遂發兵，又詐琅邪王澤發其國兵，并將而西。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "產、祿等 遣大將軍灌嬰將兵擊之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "嬰至滎陽，使人諭齊王與連和，待呂氏變而共誅之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "太尉勃與丞相平謀，以曲周侯酈商子寄與祿善，使人劫商令寄紿說祿曰：「高帝與呂后共定天下，劉氏所 立九王，呂氏所立三王，皆大臣之議。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "事以布告諸侯王，諸侯王以為宜。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "今太后崩，帝少，足下不急之國守藩，乃為上將將兵留此，為大臣諸侯所疑。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "何不速歸將軍 印，以兵屬太尉，請梁王亦歸相國印，與大臣盟而之國？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "齊兵必罷，大臣得安，足下高枕而王千里，此萬世之利也。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "祿然其計，使人報產及諸呂老人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "或以為不 便，計猶豫未有所決。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "祿信寄，與俱出遊，過其姑呂嬃。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "嬃怒曰：「奴為將而棄軍，呂氏今無處矣！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "乃悉出珠玉寶器散堂下，曰：「無為它人守也！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "八月庚申，平陽侯窋行御史大夫事，見相國產計事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "郎中令賈壽使從齊來，因數產曰：「王不早之國，今 雖欲行，尚可得邪？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "具以灌嬰與齊楚合從狀告產。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "平陽侯窋聞其語，馳告丞相平、太尉勃。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "勃欲入北軍，不得入。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "襄平侯紀通尚符節，乃令持節矯內勃北軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "勃復 令酈寄、典客劉揭說祿，曰：「帝使太尉守北軍，欲令足下之國，急歸將軍印辭去。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "不然，禍且起。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "祿遂解印屬典客，而以兵授太尉勃。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "勃入軍門，行令軍中曰： 「為呂氏右袒，為劉氏左袒。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "軍皆左袒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "勃遂將北軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "然尚有南軍，丞相平召朱虛侯章佐勃。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "勃令章監軍門，令平陽侯告衛尉，毋內相國產殿門。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "產不知祿已去北 軍，入未央宮欲為亂。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "殿門弗內，徘徊往來。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "平陽侯馳語太尉勃，勃尚恐不勝，未敢誦言誅之，乃謂朱虛侯章曰：「急入宮衛帝。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "章從勃請卒千人，入未央宮掖 門，見產廷中。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "日餔時，遂擊產。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "產走。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "天大風，從官亂，莫敢鬥者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "逐產，殺之郎中府吏舍廁中。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "章已殺產，帝令謁者持節勞章。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "章欲奪節，謁者不肯，章乃從與載，因節信馳斬長樂衛尉呂更始。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "還入北軍，復報太尉勃。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "勃起拜賀章，曰：「所患獨產，今已誅，天下定矣。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "辛酉，",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "殺呂祿，笞殺呂嬃。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "分部悉捕諸呂男女，無少長皆斬之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "大臣相與陰謀，以為少帝及三弟為王者皆非孝惠子，復共誅之，尊立文帝。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "語在周勃、高五王傳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "贊曰：孝惠、高后之時，海內得離戰國之苦，君臣俱欲無為，故惠帝拱己，高后女主制政，不出房闥，而天下晏然，刑罰罕用，民務稼穡，衣食滋殖。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}